  "docs": "CLI UX primitives: deterministic progress, tables, JSONL, and small rich-layout helpers (pinned via arch/cli).\n\nModules:\n- std.cli.profile\n- std.cli.progress\n- std.cli.table\n- std.cli.jsonl\n- std.cli.panel\n- std.cli.bar\n- std.cli.status\n- std.cli.section\n- std.cli.kv\n- std.cli.layout\n- std.cli.term\n- std.cli.events\n- std.cli.tests\n\nUsage:\n- Add dependency: x07 pkg add ext-cli-ux@0.1.4\n- Load profile from arch: std.cli.profile.from_arch_v1\n- Render progress: std.cli.progress.render_v1\n- Render tables: std.cli.table.render_v1\n- Emit JSONL: std.cli.jsonl.encode_v1\n- Render panels: std.cli.panel.render_v1\n- Render score bars: std.cli.bar.render_v1\n- Render status labels: std.cli.status.render_v1\n- Render sections: std.cli.section.render_v1\n- Render key/value rows: std.cli.kv.render_v1\n- Render columns: std.cli.layout.columns_v1\n- Render JSONL event stream: std.cli.events.render_jsonl_v1\n",
